|GKB-- Spirit Aura -----------------------------------------------|000

This simple Marken invocation allows a druid a glimpse of the
target creature's aura.  By reading the spiritual
aura, the druid can tell whether or not a creature
is in balance.  At higher levels of mastery, the
reading becomes more precise, and the druid begins
to gain more information.  At the highest level of
mastery, the druid has enough skill to judge the
creature's strength in comparison to his own.

|CKBCommand:      |000 aura <target> (defaults to attacker)
|CKBBase Cost:    |000 10 Marken nwyfre
|CKBBase Recovery:|000 fast
|CKBBase Effect:  |000 information (creature)
|CKBBase Duration:|000 instant
|CKBGuild Level:  |000 1
